export  FLASK_ENV = development         is   used  to set the  environment as  development environment

in this environment we get live debugger in the serverpage 

jinja way is used to define the variable in a file is   {{ }}

to store any input value in a variable of rendering file and retrieve value from the file we use 
        render_template("my.html"    , myn = name  , myc = cn)      here myn , myc are variables

and in my.html
            myname is {{myn}}
            mycompany is {{myc}}


then the value of myn and myc  will store in the variable  myn , myc in the file my.html  and  the file will send 
    as response to specified route 